<p style="text-align: center;"><em>From </em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/3214/9781250278319" class="external" target="_blank">Progress: How One Idea Built Civilization and Now Threatens to Destroy It</a><em>. Used with the permission of the publisher, St. Martin&#8217;s Press. Copyright © 2025 by Samuel Miller McDonald.</em></p>
